  "title": "Sales And Marketing Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location:</strong> Singapore<br />\n<strong>Type:</strong> Full-Time<br />\n<strong>Company:</strong> MB Global Marketing</p><p>🧭 About Us</p><p>At MB Global Marketing, we’re redefining how brands connect with audiences. As we scale our operations, we’re looking for a sharp, organized, and proactive <strong>Sales Operations Management Assistant</strong> to help streamline our sales processes and empower our team to perform at their best.</p><p>🎯 What You’ll Do</p><p>As our Sales Operations Management Assistant, you’ll be the backbone of our sales infrastructure. You’ll work closely with leadership to optimize workflows, manage tools, and ensure our sales team has everything they need to close deals and grow revenue.</p><p>Key Responsibilities</p><ul><li>Maintain and update CRM systems (e.g., HubSpot, Salesforce) with accurate sales data</li><li>Generate performance reports and dashboards to support strategic decisions</li><li>Assist in lead tracking, pipeline management, and sales forecastingCoordinate onboarding and training for new sales hires</li><li>Support cross-functional collaboration between sales, marketing, and operationsManage sales enablement tools and troubleshoot issues</li><li>Organize and maintain documentation including contracts, proposals, and SOPs</li></ul><p></p><ul><li>🛠️ What You Bring</li><li><ul><li>1–3 years of experience in sales operations, sales support, or administrative roles</li><li>Strong organizational and time management skills</li><li>Excellent communication and problem-solving abilities</li><li>Detail-oriented mindset with a passion for process improvement</li><li>Bonus: Experience in marketing or startup environments</li></ul><p>🌟 Why Join Us</p><ul><li>Be part of a fast-growing, creative team with global ambitions</li><li>Work directly with leadership and make a real impact</li><li>Competitive salary + performance incentives</li><li>Opportunities for growth and professional development</li><li>A culture that values innovation, ownership, and collaboration</li></ul></li></ul>",
